/**
 * Pool is the cache pool of the proton engine, it is very important.
 *
 * get(target, params, uid)
 *  Class
 *    uid = Puid.getId -> Puid save target cache
 *    target.__puid = uid
 *
 *  body
 *    uid = Puid.getId -> Puid save target cache
 *
 *
 * expire(target)
 *  cache[target.__puid] push target
 *
